// Manual approach
let clamped_manual =
  if x < 0 { 0 } else if x > 100 { 100 } else { x }

// Idiomatic approach
let clamped = math.clamp(x, min: 0, max: 100)
```

Both produce the same result; prefer `math.clamp` for clarity and correctness.

